  m_Name: QuestionChoice4
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::QuestionChoiceData
  Question: The Wolf reaches into his fur and pulls out a glowing stone. "We can
    talk even when the moon is hidden. Just tell me your secret frequency so I can
    call you whenever the 'noise' gets too loud.
  option1: "I don\u2019t give out my private frequency. If you need help, you can
    talk to the Starry Merchant in the village."
  option2: "I suppose it\u2019s okay since you\u2019re a Celestial creature like
    me. Here is my number."
  option3: I'll give it to you, but only if you promise to only call me during the
    Day phase.
